message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.IR", "cs.AI", "cs.CL", "cs.LG", and "cs.SI". The paper discusses a hybrid approach for a Semantic question answering retrieval system using Ontology Similarity and Fuzzy logic, which is relevant to Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
